name: Average Build Time
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JENKINS:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'BUILD' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN COALESCE(Avg(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as avgOutput

name: Total Number of Builds
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JENKINS:DATA) RETURN count(n) as TotalNumberBuild

name: Number of Successful Builds
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JENKINS:DATA) WHERE n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN count(n) as TotalNumberBuild

name: Number of Failed Builds
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JENKINS:DATA) WHERE n.SPKstatus='Failure' RETURN count(n) as TotalNumberBuild

name: Maximum Build Time
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JENKINS:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'BUILD' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN COALESCE(Max(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as minMaxOutput

name: Minimum Build Time
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JENKINS:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'BUILD' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN COALESCE(Min(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as minMaxOutput

name: Average Duration of Succesful Deployments
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:RUNDECK:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'DEPLOYMENT' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN COALESCE(Avg(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as avarageDeploymentDuration

name: Total Failed Deployments
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:RUNDECK:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'DEPLOYMENT' AND n.SPKstatus='Failure' RETURN count(n.SPKstatus) as totalDeploymentCount

name: Maximum Deployment Time
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:RUNDECK:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'DEPLOYMENT' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN COALESCE(Max(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as minMaxOutput

name: Total Successful Deployments
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:RUNDECK:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'DEPLOYMENT' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN count(n.SPKstatus) as totalDeploymentCount

name: Minimum Deployment Time
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:RUNDECK:DATA) WHERE n.SPKvector = 'DEPLOYMENT' and n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN COALESCE(Min(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as minMaxOutput

name: Average Complexity
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN  COALESCE(Avg(toInt(n.SPKcomplexity)),0) as AvgComplexityCoverage

name: Average Duplicated Blocks
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN  COALESCE(Avg(toInt(n.SPKduplication)),0) as AvgDuplicateBlocksCoverage

name: Number of Quality Passed Blocks
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKqualityGate='pass' RETURN count(n) as NumberOfQualityBlocks

name: Number of Quality Failed Blocks
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKqualityGate='fail' RETURN count(n) as NumberOfQualityBlocks

name: Average Code Coverage
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN  COALESCE(Avg(toInt(n.SPKcoverage)),0) as AvgCodeCoverage

name: Number of Successful Sonar Executions
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKstatus='Success' RETURN count(n) as NumberOfSonarExecutions

name: Number of Failed Sonar Executions
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:SONAR:DATA) where n.SPKstatus='Failure' RETURN count(n) as NumberOfSonarExecutions

name: Number of Defects
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JIRA:DATA) WHERE n.SPKissueType='Bug' RETURN count(n) as totalDefect

name: Number of Closed Defects
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JIRA:DATA) WHERE n.SPKissueType='Bug' and n.SPKstatus='Closed'  RETURN count(n) as ClosedDefect

name: Number of Open Defects
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JIRA:DATA) WHERE n.SPKissueType='Bug' and n.SPKstatus='Open'  RETURN count(n) as OpenDefect

name: Average Defect Duration
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:JIRA:DATA) WHERE n.SPKissueType='Bug' and n.SPKstatus='Closed'  RETURN COALESCE(Avg(toInt(n.SPKduration)),0) as AvgBuildTime

name: User with most Commits
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:GIT:DATA) RETURN count(n) as userCommitCount order by userCommitCount desc limit 1

name: Total number Release Plan Estimate in Rally
neo4jQuery: MATCH (n:RALLY_STORY) WHERE exists(n.releasePlanEstimate) RETURN sum(n.releasePlanEstimate) as releasePlanEstimate  order by releasePlanEstimate desc limit 1
